						               													<description>A quick Tabletop Roleplaying game, Heroes Cove has you choose a race and a class and then you can go on quests with others, or you can work by yourself. The standard game takes you though seven quests, but you can do more or less depending on how much time you want to play. The game comes with 40 quests so you can replay many times without repeats.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You need to go to one of the four shops to gather the needed quest items to beat the pirates, repair the bridge or other tasks needed by the townsfolk. Ultimately, whomever does the best will attract the attention of better trainers and gain more Victory Points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each round the players will have two actions. There are several different things that can be done, if you have an item needed for a quest you can contribute that item. You can grab an individual quest or you can go shopping for items.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game comes with 4 shops, the Tavern, the Blacksmith, the Armorsmith and the General Store. Each quest will require you to visit these different shops to find the items needed. Future expansions will add new shops and new quests!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
